title: Babes Ice Cream
description: Usually offers at least 2 flavors of vegan ice cream along with labeled vegan suitable toppings. Owner will help you create a vegan sundae, cone or shake. Freezer has vegan ice cream sandwiches, ice cream cakes and slices of cake, plus you could order a vegan cake. All of the cookies, brownies and cakes are made by East Side Ovens vegan bakery. Open hours vary by season - call ahead.
